To consider Fund Raising. Pursuant to the provisions of Regulation 29 and other applicable regulations of the SEBI Listing Regulations, we write to inform you that a Meeting of the Board of Directors of PCBL Limited ( the Company ) is scheduled to be held on Wednesday, the 27th day of March, 2024, inter alia, to consider and approve the proposal for raising of funds by way of issue of one or more instruments/ securities and determination of issue price thereof as may be permitted under applicable laws, subject to such regulatory/statutory approvals as may be required including the approval of the Members of the Company.
